# QA Portfolio – Paulo Victor Marques

## 📋 Project Overview
This project demonstrates **Manual QA Testing** skills using the [SauceDemo](https://saucedemo.com) web application.

*   **Scope:** Login functionality, Product Inventory, Cart Operations, and Checkout Process.
*   **Testing Types:** Manual, Functional, and Exploratory Testing.
*   **Environment:** Google Chrome (Desktop).

